  26 Apr 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> dracut-9999.ebuild:
  Call emake doc in src_compile().  Install html doc in src_install().

  26 Apr 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> dracut-9999.ebuild:
  Synced with sys-kernel/dracut-018::gentoo. Moreover I've added asciidoc build
  dependency and removed use of WITH_SWITCH_ROOT variables.

  26 Apr 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org>
  files/dracut-9999-multipath-udev-rules.patch:
  Rebased multipath-udev-rules.patch against current dracut git-HEAD.

  25 Mar 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> dracut-9999.ebuild:
  Synced with sys-kernel/dracut-017-r1::gentoo again.

  02 Mar 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> dracut-9999.ebuild,
  -files/dracut-9999-usrmount-fsck-fix.patch, metadata.xml:
  Synced with sys-kernel/dracut-017-r1::gentoo.

  12 Jan 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> dracut-9999.ebuild,
  +files/dracut-9999-usrmount-fsck-fix.patch:
  Test fix for bug #396575.

  12 Jan 2012; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> dracut-9999.ebuild:
  Synced with sys-kernel/dracut-014 in Portage tree.

  24 Nov 2011; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> dracut-9999.ebuild:
  Reverted URI to git.kernel.org.

  Removed no-herd btw.

  22 Sep 2011; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> dracut-9999.ebuild:
  Changed git.kernel.org URL temporary to upstream's mirror for kernel.org
  down-time.

  07 Sep 2011; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> dracut-9999.ebuild:
  Synced with sys-kernel/dracut-013 in Portage tree.

  10 Aug 2011; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> dracut-9999.ebuild:
  Updated to changes after 011 release:
  - adding/removing modules
  - repo has been moved from sf.net to kernel.org

  Moreover ebuild has been migrated to git-2 eclass.

  07 Mar 2011; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org> dracut-9999.ebuild,
  +files/dracut-9999-multipath-udev-rules.patch, metadata.xml:
  Updated according to changes in dracut-008-r1 in the main tree. Getting
  source from original dracut repo, branch - master.

  11 Sep 2010; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@aidecoe.name> dracut-9999.ebuild:
  Depend on >=baselayout-1.12.13-r1 (only in my overlay at this time).  System
  won't boot with earlier because Dracut mounts devpts and <=baselayout-1.12.13
  doesn't check if it's already mounted.

  Moreover removed unnecessary version specifications for dependencies.  Only
  mandatory are left.

  10 Sep 2010; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@aidecoe.name> -dracut-006-r2.ebuild,
  -dracut-007-r1.ebuild, -files/dracut-006-console_init-not-necessary.patch,
  -files/dracut-006-dhcp6.patch, -files/dracut-006-dm-udev-rules.patch,
  -files/dracut-006-lc-all-c.patch, -files/dracut-007-dm-udev-rules.patch,
  -files/dracut-007-multipath-udev-rules.patch:
  Removed ebuilds (with corresponding patches) already committed to Portage
  tree.  dracut-006-r2 is committed as dracut-006-r1 and dracut-007-r1 is
  committed as dracut-007.

  10 Sep 2010; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@aidecoe.name> dracut-9999.ebuild:
  Latest changes in dracut-007-r1 ported to dracut-9999. Moreover it closes
  bug #298014 by restricting test.

  10 Sep 2010; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@aidecoe.name> dracut-007-r1.ebuild:
  Fixes bug #334347 (dm related dependencies) - thanks to Akos Szalkai
  <szalkai@szalkai.net> for report and patch.

  16 Aug 2010; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@aidecoe.name> dracut-9999.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Added plymouth dependency and USE flag.

*dracut-007-r1 (16 Aug 2010)
*dracut-006-r2 (16 Aug 2010)

  16 Aug 2010; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@aidecoe.name> +dracut-007-r1.ebuild,
  +dracut-006-r2.ebuild, -dracut-006-r1.ebuild, -dracut-007.ebuild,
  dracut-9999.ebuild:
  Removed masked dependencies in release ebuilds and fixed other QA warnings
  in all ebuilds.  Added warning about dhcp-4 not working with QEMU.  Ebuilds
  with QA warnings (except of 9999) were removed.

*dracut-007 (09 Aug 2010)

  09 Aug 2010; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@aidecoe.name> +dracut-007.ebuild,
  +files/dracut-007-dm-udev-rules.patch,
  +files/dracut-007-multipath-udev-rules.patch, metadata.xml:
  Version bump.  Ebuild is copied from dracut-9999.ebuild.  There were just
  removed lines related to git repo and added patches from gentoo branch as
  separate files.

  09 Aug 2010; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@aidecoe.name> dracut-9999.ebuild:
  New module and corresponding USE flag - gensplash - added.

  Updated run-time dependencies:
    - added media-gfx/splashutils for gensplash USE flag

  08 Aug 2010; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@aidecoe.name> dracut-9999.ebuild:
  Removed keywords.

  06 Aug 2010; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@aidecoe.name> dracut-9999.ebuild:
  New module and corresponding USE flag - bootchart - added.

  Updated run-time dependencies:
    - removed unnecessary sys-auth/nss-mdns
    - removed sys-boot/plymouth (no Plymouth ebuild yet)
    - added app-benchmarks/bootchart for bootchart USE flag

  Dracut doesn't need any dependencies in the build-time except of few to
  convert DocBook documents into the Unix man page format.  That's why all
  previous run-time dependencies were removed from DEPEND and added DocBook
  related.

*dracut-9999 (27 Jul 2010)
*dracut-006-r1 (27 Jul 2010)
*dracut-006 (27 Jul 2010)

  27 Jul 2010; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@aidecoe.name> +dracut-006.ebuild,
  +files/dracut-006-dhcp6.patch, +files/dracut-006-lc-all-c.patch,
  +dracut-006-r1.ebuild, +files/dracut-006-dm-udev-rules.patch,
  +files/dracut-006-console_init-not-necessary.patch, +dracut-9999.ebuild,
  +metadata.xml:
  Ebuilds moved from my local overlay. Version 006 is slightly updated
  dracut-004.ebuild maintained by Lance Albertson. Later 006-r1 is refactorized
  of the previous and includes new patches. Version 9999 is customized to my
  fork of Dracut on GitHub. Version 006 (bug #324705) is already in official
  Portage tree.  006-r1 is included in bug #329003 and waits for Ramereth's
  acceptance.

  See ChangeLog in Portage tree for full history of Dracut ebuilds.
